			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">Yes and very! Our platform is stored on Microsoft Azure and we practice industry standards for security and data backups. We can provide detailed specifics upon request.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item">
			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item-header">
				<h3 class="tech-u-accordion-wide__title">Is there a free trial available?</h3>
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__indicator">{{> icons/minus}}{{> icons/plus}}</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">No, this is not something we offer. We personally guide new customers through the configuration, installation, and training of the platform. Historically we’ve found that playing around with a free trial results in very slow uptake throughout your facility - our goal is to get you fully functioning in 90 days or less.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item">
			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item-header">
				<h3 class="tech-u-accordion-wide__title">Can I use my on-site servers?</h3>
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__indicator">{{> icons/minus}}{{> icons/plus}}</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">It is technically possible though very rare. If you must use an on-site server we will need to discuss a custom maintenance plan for your needs.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item">
			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item-header">
				<h3 class="tech-u-accordion-wide__title">Is this a monthly subscription, or how do we pay for this system?</h3>
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__indicator">{{> icons/minus}}{{> icons/plus}}</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">Yes, as a SaaS there is a monthly subscription cost. We only charge for Compass stations while access to HQ and every User is free. Billing can also be done quarterly, bi-annually or annually.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item">
			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item-header">
				<h3 class="tech-u-accordion-wide__title">Is your edge device included in the price?</h3>
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__indicator">{{> icons/minus}}{{> icons/plus}}</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">No, Trackers are optional and sold (or leased) separately.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item">
			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item-header">
				<h3 class="tech-u-accordion-wide__title">Do I own my data? What about my designs?</h3>
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__indicator">{{> icons/minus}}{{> icons/plus}}</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">Absolutely yes! All data and work instructions are your property. More information on this is provided in our Terms of Service.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item">
			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item-header">
				<h3 class="tech-u-accordion-wide__title">What does the Smart Tool integration look like?</h3>
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__indicator">{{> icons/minus}}{{> icons/plus}}</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">Smart Tool integration can be a vast offering. From commercial tools to even home-built equipment. Ultimately, the integration is looking for validation that the appropriate action has taken place.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
