			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__item-header">
				<h3 class="tech-u-accordion-wide__title">Can my operators sign in at more than one station?</h3>
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__indicator">{{> icons/minus}}{{> icons/plus}}</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__body">
				<div class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-item">
					<p class="tech-u-accordion-wide__list-title">Yes they can, but this will lead to doubling their Applied Hours in the system. If this is common in your facility, inform your Customer Success Representative and they will review the best practices with you and your team.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
